-------------------------
Employee Records System
-------------------------

Program to manage a company's employee records

Features
--------
 - add an employee
 - fire an employee
 - promote an employee
 - view all employees, past and present
 - view current employees
 - view former employees

Hierarchy
---------
 - Employee class : encapsulates the informations describing one single employee
  - Database class : manages all the employees of the company
  - UserInterface class : provides the menu-based interface for interactivity for the user


---------------------------------------------------------------
program inspired by the book C++ professionnal by Marc Gregoire
 